    <comment>- update to 20241021:
  * Stop breaking surrogate pairs in `toDelta()`
  * Start tracking new upstream https://github.com/dmsnell/diff-match-patch (#17)
  * Removed `imp` usage in speedtest
  * Updated dev dependencies, use uv for dev workflows when
    available (#22)
  * Tested on Python 3.8-3.13
  * Untested on Python 3.7, will be unsupported in future release</comment>
